{"id": "ChIJd5kcCeDbwoARm1Uoi-M2LJY", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 163, "displayName": {"text": "MAMA XITA BBQ Temple City", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJd5kcCeDbwoARm1Uoi-M2LJY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204M2MwTm5NMDFhT1ZRMVFsTXROVGM0VkhGTmMyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It was great to visit this place with my family. I’ve always been a fan of Mama Xita back in China, so I was excited to try this location, and it did not disappoint!\n\nThe atmosphere is welcoming, and the staff are incredibly friendly and attentive. Joshua took great care of us throughout the evening and made our experience even more enjoyable.\n\nOur party of four ordered the 2–3 person combo, along with the thick-cut beef tongue, spicy chicken feet, and pineapple finger meat. Everything was delicious, but the thick-cut beef tongue was definitely the standout dish for me. It was cooked perfectly—juicy, tender, and packed with flavor.\n\nThe house special sauce was also excellent. It leans toward the sweeter side, but you can ask for less sugar if you prefer a less sweet flavor profile.\n\nAs someone who doesn’t eat a huge amount, I actually prefer this concept over some AYCE options because you can order exactly what you want without feeling like you’re overcommitting. Overall, we had a fantastic experience and will definitely be coming back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It was great to visit this place with my family. I’ve always been a fan of Mama Xita back in China, so I was excited to try this location, and it did not disappoint!\n\nThe atmosphere is welcoming, and the staff are incredibly friendly and attentive. Joshua took great care of us throughout the evening and made our experience even more enjoyable.\n\nOur party of four ordered the 2–3 person combo, along with the thick-cut beef tongue, spicy chicken feet, and pineapple finger meat. Everything was delicious, but the thick-cut beef tongue was definitely the standout dish for me. It was cooked perfectly—juicy, tender, and packed with flavor.\n\nThe house special sauce was also excellent. It leans toward the sweeter side, but you can ask for less sugar if you prefer a less sweet flavor profile.\n\nAs someone who doesn’t eat a huge amount, I actually prefer this concept over some AYCE options because you can order exactly what you want without feeling like you’re overcommitting. Overall, we had a fantastic experience and will definitely be coming back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "jingjing fang", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112632857477968131828/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLppgE6H2V6JOmCirnnNdv5zG3nmkFa9I56JbZVb5BrF12ThQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-23T04:18:50.961307651Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204M2MwTm5NMDFhT1ZRMVFsTXROVGM0VkhGTmMyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT204M2MwTm5NMDFhT1ZRMVFsTXROVGM0VkhGTmMyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2dbe0091c9977:0x962c36e38b28559b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJd5kcCeDbwoARm1Uoi-M2LJY/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2poQ1kyTXlaVGQxVlRrNFVsaHdaMVprY3kxa1JrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Really enjoyed the food here! The meat quality was great and everything tasted fresh. Service was friendly and the atmosphere was nice. Definitely a place I'd come back to again. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really enjoyed the food here! The meat quality was great and everything tasted fresh. Service was friendly and the atmosphere was nice. Definitely a place I'd come back to again. Highly recommend!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Grey Song", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/co